A machine-readable bill of materials (CycloneDX SBOM) with the resolved license
of every dependency is generated at release time (EFF-16). To regenerate it:

    cargo cyclonedx --format json   # or: cargo deny check licenses

GPL-3.0-or-later is compatible with MPL-2.0 and the permissive licenses above
(the combined work is distributable under GPL-3.0-or-later). No bundled
dependency imposes a license incompatible with GPL-3.0-or-later; should one be
introduced, the `cargo deny check licenses` gate (EFF-16) fails the build.

